TITLE: Layer-Tap Behavior Binding Example
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to bind the `&lt` behavior to a key. When the key is held, layer 3 is activated. When tapped, the SPACE keycode is sent. This assumes that `&lt` is a predefined layer-tap behavior.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zmkfirmware/zmk/blob/main/docs/docs/keymaps/behaviors/hold-tap.mdx#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: dts
CODE:
```
&lt 3 SPACE
```

