TITLE: Modifier Definition for Mod-Morph in ZMK
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to define the modifiers that trigger the morphed behavior of a mod-morph. It specifies the modifiers using a bitwise OR combination.  Available modifiers include Left/Right Shift, Control, Alt, and GUI.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zmkfirmware/zmk/blob/main/docs/docs/keymaps/behaviors/mod-morph.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: dts
CODE:
```
mods = <(MOD_LGUI|MOD_LSFT|MOD_RGUI|MOD_RSFT)>;
```

