SOURCE: https://github.com/zmkfirmware/zmk/blob/main/docs/docs/keymaps/behaviors/macros.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: dts
CODE:
```
bindings
    = <&to 1>
    , <&bl BL_ON>
    , <&kp Z &kp M &kp K &kp EXCLAMATION>
    ;
```

