TITLE: Keymap - Skipping Unused Positions - DTS
DESCRIPTION: This devicetree overlay defines a keymap that corresponds to the matrix transform in the previous example. It assigns keycodes to the positions defined in the matrix transform. This allows the keyboard to function with the correct key assignments despite unused positions in the physical matrix. Requires the zmk,keymap compatible node.
