TITLE: Kscan Configuration for Unibody Keyboard
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates a Kscan configuration for a simple 3x3 macropad matrix on a unibody keyboard. It defines the GPIO pins used for scanning key presses and releases, specifying the diode direction and wakeup source.
