TITLE: Conditional Target Sources and Linker Sections CMake
DESCRIPTION: This snippet conditionally sets the target sources and linker sections based on whether the device is configured as the central or peripheral half of the split keyboard. If `CONFIG_ZMK_SPLIT_ROLE_CENTRAL` is enabled, it uses `central.c` and `zmk-split-transport-central.ld`. Otherwise, it uses `peripheral.c` and `zmk-split-transport-peripheral.ld`.
