LANGUAGE: dts
CODE:
```
&pinctrl {
    qdec_default: qdec_default {
        group1 {
            psels = <NRF_PSEL(QDEC_A, 1, 11)>,
                    <NRF_PSEL(QDEC_B, 1, 10)>;
            bias-pull-up;
        };
    };
};

