TITLE: STM32 Clock Configuration (DTS)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates configuring the clock settings for an STM32 board in the devicetree.  It configures the HSI clock, PLL, and RCC nodes. It also requires that the corresponding clock/PLL settings are removed from the `<board>_defconfig` file.  This example uses the HSI clock as the PLL source.
