LANGUAGE: dts
CODE:
```
&clk_hsi {
  status = "okay";
};

&pll {
  prediv = <1>;
  mul = <12>;
  clocks = <&clk_hsi>;
  status = "okay";
};

&rcc {
  clocks = <&pll>;
  clock-frequency = <DT_FREQ_M(72)>;
  ahb-prescaler = <1>;
  apb1-prescaler = <2>;
};
```

