TITLE: Defining Zephyr Linker Sources
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines Zephyr linker sources for specific sections of the firmware, including behaviors, events, and behavior local ID map, which affects how the firmware is linked and organized in memory. The linker sources are defined conditionally based on Kconfig options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zmkfirmware/zmk/blob/main/app/CMakeLists.txt#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: CMake
CODE:
```
zephyr_linker_sources(SECTIONS include/linker/zmk-behaviors.ld)
zephyr_linker_sources(RODATA include/linker/zmk-events.ld)

if(CONFIG_ZMK_BEHAVIOR_LOCAL_IDS)
