TITLE: Using Multiple Predefined Layouts in DTS
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use multiple predefined layouts, typically for a 60% keyboard with ANSI, ISO, All1u, and HHKB variants. It includes each layout's DTS file and assigns the corresponding transform and kscan nodes to each layout.
