DESCRIPTION: This code snippet configures a ZMK macro to switch layers and change the underglow color when pressed and released. It utilizes `&macro_press` for layer activation, `&macro_tap` to change the underglow, `&macro_pause_for_release` to wait for key release, and `&macro_release` to revert layer activation. The RGB color is defined using `RGB_COLOR_HSB`.
