tap-ms = <0>;
bindings
    = <&macro_press &mo 1>
    , <&macro_tap &rgb_ug RGB_COLOR_HSB(128,100,100)>
    , <&macro_pause_for_release>
    , <&macro_release &mo 1>
    , <&macro_tap &rgb_ug RGB_COLOR_HSB(300,100,50)>;

```

